Package: preregister
Title: Tools to simplify the design and pre-registration of experiments, including generating simulated data and conducting power analyses
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: person("Graeme", "Blair", email = "graeme.blair@columbia.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Experiment registration package to create a pre-registration document and describe an experimental design and planned analyses in detail.
Depends: R (>= 3.2.0)
Imports: rmarkdown
Suggests: testthat
License: GPL (>= 2)
LazyData: true
